# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Private GitLab mirror (gitlab.com/garudadev1/scanner-manager): full RE
# context, probe sessions, firmware captures, and dev tooling are tracked
# for cross-machine Cursor work. The public GitHub mirror (origin) should
# not receive these paths — use scripts/publish_github.ps1 to export a
# filtered tree; do not push context-heavy commits to origin directly.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

